{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"土地，选择了我","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":1,"day":7}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地，选择了我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张可绣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地，选择了我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我，选择了土地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的选择，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一群光秃秃的山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的选择，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一条白白流走的水；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不选择秕瘪和虚伪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我选择的是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心田上垂荡的谷粒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我曾是一碗酸菜汤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落进的一滴泪水；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我曾是割掉的“尾巴”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下的痕迹；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我曾是不是奴隶的“奴隶”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也有脑袋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也有思维，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有的都被握在一只没有老茧的手里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在柳丝穿起鸭嘴黄的小星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我选择了春风的翠绿纤维，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳金灿灿的丝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编织一件时髦的地衣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我用灼热的目光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选择了风雪的寒夜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我用彩色的思考，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选择了冻僵的土地；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不去选择汗珠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗珠，已编进历史的诗集……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地，选择了我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我，选择了土地。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}